data.title: Celebrity birthdays for the week of Aug. 11-17
data.meta_description: Celebrities having birthdays during the week of Aug. 11-17 include wrestler-actor Hulk Hogan, singer Belinda Carlisle of The Go-Go’s and actor Sean Penn.
